      <title>FreeBSD &#43; Samba 4.16 &#43; Symbolic Links 설정</title>
      <link>https://ageldama.github.io/posts/2023-11nov/2023-11nov05--freebsd-samba4-symlink/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Nov 2023 05:40:00 +0000</pubDate>
